WEBVTT

00:00,000 --> 00:04,950
Most teams blame tools for weak activity results, but execution discipline is the real gap.

00:05,000 --> 00:09,950
Without a clear review habit, metrics quality drifts even when effort increases. Measurement becomes useful when...

00:10,000 --> 00:14,950
Assign one owner, track one metric, and review one live decision every week.

00:15,000 --> 00:19,950
Use a one-week pilot to test behavior change and keep evidence from the workflow.

00:20,000 --> 00:24,950
Teams get better adoption, cleaner decisions in review, and fewer repeat corrections in delivery.

00:25,000 --> 00:29,950
Which weekly checkpoint would improve decision quality first?
